OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1772572327
OL,3,CAlan Cumming says 'we were all let
OL,4,Cdown' by 'trauma-triggering' BAFTAs
OL,6,FBAFTA host Alan Cumming described the
OL,7,Faftermath of the awards ceremony
OL,8,Fbroadcast, during which a racial slur
OL,9,Fwas aired, as "trauma triggering",
OL,10,Fsaying that "we were all let down by
OL,11,Fdecisions made to both broadcast slurs
OL,12,Fand censor free speech."
OL,14,FDuring the ceremony in London, while
OL,15,FSinners stars Delroy Lindo and Michael
OL,16,FB Jordan were presenting an award,
OL,17,FScottish campaigner John Davidson, who
OL,18,Fhas Tourette's syndrome, shouted a
OL,19,Fracial slur, which was broadcast on
OL,20,Fthe BBC.
OL,26,@qD@OOUrD@MOUtD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
