FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1772572327
OL,3,CAlan Cumming says 'we were all let
OL,4,Cdown' by 'trauma-triggering' BAFTAs
OL,6,FDuring the broadcast, Cumming
OL,7,Fapologised for the language viewers
OL,8,Fmay have heard, and in the aftermath,
OL,9,Fthe BBC apologised for not editing it
OL,10,Fout and said its executive complaints
OL,11,Funit would complete a "fast-tracked
OL,12,Finvestigation" into the incident.
OL,14,FCommenting for the first time since
OL,15,Fthe ceremony, the Scottish star, 61,
OL,16,Fwho hosted the ceremony, wrote on
OL,17,FInstagram: "It's now a week since I
OL,18,Fhosted the Baftas.
OL,26,@sD@WOUtD@NO]yD@LOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
