OL,3,CAlan Cumming says 'we were all let
OL,4,Cdown' by 'trauma-triggering' BAFTAs
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,F"What should have been an evening
OL,12,Fcelebrating creativity and inclusion
OL,13,Fturned into a trauma-triggering
OL,14,Fs***show.
OL,16,F"I'm so sorry for all the pain Black
OL,17,Fpeople have felt hearing that word
OL,18,Fechoed round the world."
OL,26,@sD@AOUxD@AOUzD@XO]
