OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1772572327
OL,3,CAlan Cumming says 'we were all let
OL,4,Cdown' by 'trauma-triggering' BAFTAs
OL,6,FDavidson was at the BAFTAs
OL,7,Frepresenting the film I Swear, which
OL,8,Fdramatises his life with severe
OL,9,FTourette syndrome.
OL,11,FHe has described feeling "mortified"
OL,12,Fby what happened and said in an
OL,13,Finterview with Variety that the BBC
OL,14,Fshould have "worked harder" to ensure
OL,15,Fhis racial slur was not broadcast.
OL,26,@sD@ZOUsD@dO]vD@MOUvD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1772572327
OL,3,CAlan Cumming says 'we were all let
OL,4,Cdown' by 'trauma-triggering' BAFTAs
OL,6,F"In addition to the announcement by
OL,7,FAlan Cumming, the BBC and Bafta, I can
OL,8,Fonly add that I am, and always have
OL,9,Fbeen deeply mortified if anyone
OL,10,Fconsiders my involuntary tics to be
OL,11,Fintentional or to carry any meaning,"
OL,12,Fhe told Variety.
OL,14,F"I was in attendance to celebrate the
OL,15,Ffilm of my life, I Swear, which more
OL,16,Fthan any film or TV documentary,
OL,17,Fexplains the origins, condition,
OL,18,Ftraits and manifestations of Tourette
OL,19,Fsyndrome.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1772572327
OL,3,CAlan Cumming says 'we were all let
OL,4,Cdown' by 'trauma-triggering' BAFTAs
OL,6,F"I have spent my life trying to
OL,7,Fsupport and empower the Tourette's
OL,8,Fcommunity and to teach empathy,
OL,9,Fkindness and understanding from others
OL,10,Fand I will continue to do so.
OL,12,F"I chose to leave the auditorium early
OL,13,Finto the ceremony as I was aware of
OL,14,Fthe distress my tics were causing."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUvD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
