PN,31807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1772572327
OL,3,CAlan Cumming says 'we were all let
OL,4,Cdown' by 'trauma-triggering' BAFTAs
OL,6,FCumming, who also hosts the US version
OL,7,Fof The Traitors, also said in his
OL,8,Fstatement: "I'm so sorry the
OL,9,FTourette's community has been reminded
OL,10,Fof the lack of understanding and
OL,11,Ftolerance that abounds regarding their
OL,12,Fcondition.
OL,14,F"The only possible good that could
OL,15,Fcome of this is a reminder that words
OL,16,Fmatter, that rushing to judgment about
OL,17,Fthings of which we are not fully
OL,18,Fcognisant is folly, that all trauma
OL,19,Fmust be recognised and honoured.
OL,26,@pD@LOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
