CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1772572327
OL,3,CAlan Cumming says 'we were all let
OL,4,Cdown' by 'trauma-triggering' BAFTAs
OL,6,F"We were all let down by decisions
OL,7,Fmade to both broadcast slurs and
OL,8,Fcensor free speech. Congratulations to
OL,9,Fall those artists whose work was
OL,10,Fovershadowed by the night's events."
OL,12,FDuring the broadcast, the BBC edited
OL,13,Fout part of a speech by My Father's
OL,14,FShadow filmmaker Akinola Davies Jr, in
OL,15,Fwhich he said "Free Palestine".
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@dO]wD@OOUwD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
