PN,31809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1772572327
OL,3,CAlan Cumming says 'we were all let
OL,4,Cdown' by 'trauma-triggering' BAFTAs
OL,6,FSpeaking on stage at the NAACP Image
OL,7,FAwards in California at the weekend,
OL,8,FLindo, who is nominated in the best
OL,9,Fsupporting actor category at the
OL,10,FOscars for his role in Ryan Coogler's
OL,11,Fvampire horror, told the audience: "We
OL,12,Fappreciate, I appreciate, all of the
OL,13,Fsupport and love we have been shown in
OL,14,Fthe aftermath of what happened last
OL,15,Fweekend, it means a lot to us.
OL,17,F"It is an honour to be here amongst
OL,18,Four people this evening, amongst so
OL,19,Fmany people who have shown us such
OL,20,Fincredible support.
OL,26,@sD@dOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
