PN,31810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1772572327
OL,3,CAlan Cumming says 'we were all let
OL,4,Cdown' by 'trauma-triggering' BAFTAs
OL,6,F"And it's a classic case of something
OL,7,Fthat could've been very negative
OL,8,Fbecoming very positive. Thank you so
OL,9,Fmuch for the support."
OL,11,FBAFTA apologised after the film awards
OL,12,Fand said it took "full responsibility"
OL,13,Ffor putting its guests in a "difficult
OL,14,Fsituation".
OL,16,FBAFTA also apologised "unreservedly"
OL,17,Fto Jordan and Lindo, and "to all those
OL,18,Fimpacted", adding: "We would like to
OL,19,Fthank Michael and Delroy for their
OL,20,Fincredible dignity and
OL,21,Fprofessionalism."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@VO]tD@ROUtD@fO]uD@]OUvD@JO]xD@
OL,26,AWOUxD@dO]yD@ZOUzD@IO]zD@TOU}D@QO]
