OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1772572327
OL,3,CAlan Cumming says 'we were all let
OL,4,Cdown' by 'trauma-triggering' BAFTAs
OL,6,FThe statement continued: "We take full
OL,7,Fresponsibility for putting our guests
OL,8,Fin a very difficult situation and we
OL,9,Fapologise to all.
OL,11,F"We will learn from this and keep
OL,12,Finclusion at the core of all we do,
OL,13,Fmaintaining our belief in film and
OL,14,Fstorytelling as a critical conduit for
OL,15,Fcompassion and empathy."
OL,26,@nD@ZOUsD@AOUwD@XO]
