OL,3,CAlan Cumming says 'we were all let
OL,4,Cdown' by 'trauma-triggering' BAFTAs
OL,6,FIn a letter to members, BAFTA
OL,7,Fchairwoman Sara Putt and chief
OL,8,Fexecutive Jane Millichip said a
OL,9,F"comprehensive" review was underway,
OL,10,Fadding: "Please rest assured how
OL,11,Fseriously we are taking this."
OL,13,FThe letter continued: "We take full
OL,14,Fresponsibility for putting our guests
OL,15,Fand members of the academy in a very
OL,16,Fdifficult situation and we will learn
OL,17,Ffrom this.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@OO]rD@IOUsD@^O]uD@WOU
