OL,6,F"We will keep inclusion at the core of
OL,7,Fall we do, maintaining our belief in
OL,8,Ffilm and storytelling as a critical
OL,9,Fconduit for compassion and empathy `
OL,10,Fas firmly demonstrated by this year's
OL,11,Fnominated and winning films."
